Package net.mtrop.doom.object

Contains object interfaces for most data.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BinaryObject
    Common elements of all objects that are loaded from binary data.
    BinaryObject.Transformer<BO extends BinaryObject>
    Transformer interface for transform calls.
    GraphicObject
    Interface for graphic data.
    TextObject
    Common elements of all objects that are loaded from text data.
    TextObject.Transformer<TO extends TextObject>
    Transformer interface for transform calls.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryObject.InlineScanner<BO extends BinaryObject>
    A deserializing scanner iterator that returns the same object instance with its contents changed.
    BinaryObject.Reflect  
    BinaryObject.Scanner<BO extends BinaryObject>
    A deserializing scanner iterator that returns independent instances of objects.

    TextObject.Reflect
